    • 方法详细资料

      • create

        void create(AbstractElement element)
        Creates an entry in the database for the element.
        参数:
        element - an unsaved element (the "id" will be updated after method is invoked)

      • delete

        void delete(File file)
        Removes a file from the database for the specified element.
        参数:
        file - the file to remove (cannot be null)

      • update

        void update(File file)
        Modifies a file in the database.
        参数:
        file - the file to update (cannot be null)

      • findElements

        AbstractElement[] findElements(Directory directory)
        Locates elements in the database which appear under the presented directory
        参数:
        directory - the directory (cannot be null - use Directory.ROOT_DIRECTORY for root)
        返回:
        zero or more elements in the directory (an empty array may be returned - never null)
